                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Last page. Standard item. Are any residents matching this sketch currently - hold on. Hold still. The sketch is bad. But you match it. There is a memo stapled to it, and the memo says do not engage, report immediately. And yet here we both are, engaging."
                        }
                    ],
