                            Label: "refuse_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Good day, resident. Resident Verification Survey, on behalf of verified trust and verified value. Three items today: household size, nether star holdings on premises, and one final item on the last page. Participation is voluntary. Noncompliance is noted."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "This is a routine canvass of the Sango approach. Verified households enjoy verified benefits. Unverified households enjoy follow-up visits. Shall we begin?"
                        }
                    ],
